# videoconverter
## Simple Gem For Video Processing

## Compatibility:

## Ruby:
Tested with ruby 2.0

## streamio-ffmpeg:
 The current gem is tested against streamio-ffmpeg 1.0.0.

## Require the gem
```
 require 'rubygems'
 require 'videoconverter'
```
## Usage :
```
options =  {
            "source_url" => 'http://www.xyz.com/video.mp4',
            "actions" => {
                          "resolution" => "320x240",
                          "video_bitrate" => 92,
                          "thumbnail" => 10,
                          "split" => 3,
                          "cut" => "00:00:10-00:01:10"
                         },
            "dir" => "/home/videos/"
           }

VideoConverter.process(options)
```
## Splitting videos in equal parts
```
"actions" => {
              "split" => 3
             }
```
The value is number of equal parts

## Thumbnail of video
```
"actions" => {
              "thumbnail" => 10
             }
```
the value is provided in seconds


